Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的越南战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克 你在这里等著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯哥哥你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看外面出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 但歌声...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍它 砍它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丛林天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯 里克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是最棒的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 清醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于见到那一天的你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次 与我共舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 Let's dance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对小夜做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克娜拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克娜拉小姐振作一点  克娜拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 把你给...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:09:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道你还藏着那么一手 真希望你能早点使出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克娜拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 把集装箱给...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒那些把孩子们弄成这模样的家伙们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你才可以守卫我们的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了明天过好今天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有你才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事只有你才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正是为此而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「红盾」一直持续进行着这样的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 和阿姨一起去天国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我必须去做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我一定马上回来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯哥哥 好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里现在究竟发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 你问那个人比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔 你这家伙究竟在搞什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易可以爽快的杀掉小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一个人类居然把我的小夜...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使正常战斗 她也不是那么容易死去的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好还是别太小看她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥不是也这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要赶紧运走「歌之女神」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她马上就要到这里来...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是 武士？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔 万事小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集完卡尔和武士的情报之后再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克 里克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 凯哥哥他一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么严重吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟会变成怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 不用担心 我一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细的事情之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之快从这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊 凯哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牡她什么问题都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她什么问题都没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追那架直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:16:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「红盾」 想要阻碍我们计划的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你真是坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情报应该事先告诉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔用过「DELTA-67」这件事你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他的病状是目前为止没有出现过的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个不是「DELTA-67」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不吃惊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 因为我看惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后我一直 满心期待着你觉醒的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牡 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么自己会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多事情我回忆不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多事情我不想回忆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你们...在这里想对孩子们所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我变得不再是我 也绝对要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「幽灵」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「幽灵」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 牡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牡 变回以前 她能变回以前的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能变回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:20:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信吗 你相信奇迹的存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我相信那种东西 现在一定在侍奉神明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...一辈子都不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管别人怎么说小夜都是我们的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让她任凭你们摆布了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你把有关小夜的一切都告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始由我来保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 究竟是谁的错 为什么事情会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小夜姐姐必须战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你不用再隐瞒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要一个人背负所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友是同属于田径部的音无小夜
